ot\subset \mathrm{NC}^k$. 9. $\mathrm{PIT} \in \mathrm{DTIME}[n^{\mathrm{poly}(\log \log n)}]$ or $ orall \epsilon,  orall k, \mathrm{NTIME}[2^{n^{\epsilon}}] 
